162
00:07:26,547 --> 00:07:27,558
Ian.

163
00:07:28,291 --> 00:07:29,480
Tu vas lui parler ?

164
00:07:32,008 --> 00:07:33,293
Il a des fleurs.

165
00:07:33,457 --> 00:07:34,509
